OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,FOne of the country's best kept secrets
OL,7,Fis undergoing a once-in-a-decade
OL,8,Frevamp, as 17 tonnes of chalk are laid
OL,9,Fonto the Cerne Abbas Giant.
OL,11,FThe Giant, whose origin remains a
OL,12,Fmystery, undergoes a revamp every
OL,13,Fseven to 10 years but work is starting
OL,14,Fearlier this year due to climate
OL,15,Fchange and changing weather patterns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
