OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,FThe Dorset landmark has been under
OL,7,FNational Trust ownership for over a
OL,8,Fcentury and every decade dozens of
OL,9,Ftheir staff and volunteers spend
OL,10,Faround 300 hours renewing the 55-metre
OL,11,F(180ft) tall chalk outline.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,FLuke Dawson, lead ranger at the
OL,7,FNational Trust's West Dorset &
OL,8,FCranborne Chase area of natural
OL,9,Fbeauty, said: "We want to keep on top
OL,10,Fof it because we're seeing that it's
OL,11,Fstarting to overgrow a lot more and
OL,12,Ffade, and it's something that people
OL,13,Fhave travelled from all over the
OL,14,Fcountry to come and see, and the world
OL,15,Feven in some instances."
OL,17,FThe lengthy renewal begins with cattle
OL,18,Fgrazing on Giant Hill, which removes
OL,19,Fthe surrounding grass, and allows the
OL,20,Ffigure to remain visible.
OL,26,@qD@OOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
