FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,FThe former layer of chalk is then
OL,7,Fremoved, with sharp outlines carved by
OL,8,Frangers and their team using spades,
OL,9,Ffollowed by the re-chalking.
OL,11,FThe steep hill, sloping at a gradient
OL,12,Fof around one in three, is vulnerable
OL,13,Fto erosion and requires the chalk to
OL,14,Fbe packed tightly by hand to avoid
OL,15,Fwater damage, weeds and algae from
OL,16,Fforming.
OL,18,FIn previous years, the re-chalking
OL,19,Fprocess would usually take place in
OL,20,FSeptember, but have started earlier
OL,21,Fdue to changes in weather patterns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,FIn 2019, just days after laying fresh
OL,7,Fchalk, intense rainfall washed it away.
OL,9,F"The erosion was in part because of
OL,10,Fthat September rain," Mr Dawson said.
OL,12,F"With the algae, it's one that we just
OL,13,Fcan't predict.
OL,15,F"If that algae does not get killed off
OL,16,Fover winter, coupled with the fact
OL,17,Fthat we're getting wetter summers, it
OL,18,Fjust promotes that algal growth in
OL,19,Fdamp conditions.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@UO]tD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,F"Rather than a nice white chalk sheen,
OL,7,Fyou are getting a dull grey-green kind
OL,8,Fof sheen like slime, so it's something
OL,9,Fwe have got to constantly check."
OL,11,FThe National Trust this year decided
OL,12,Fto carry the work out in May and trial
OL,13,Fa new technique which consists of
OL,14,Fmixing the chalk with water to create
OL,15,Fa plaster of Paris-type consistency
OL,16,Fbefore laying it down.
OL,18,FThe origin of the figure is unknown
OL,19,Fand continues to fuel debates.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
