PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,FWhile local records only register its
OL,7,Fexistence in the 17th Century, in
OL,8,F2021, carbon dating analysis proved
OL,9,Fits existence around 700 to 1100 AD.
OL,11,FScott Welland, visitor, operations and
OL,12,Fexperience manager at the National
OL,13,FTrust in West Dorset, said: "One
OL,14,Ftheory is that during that period, the
OL,15,Fgrass grew back.
OL,17,F"So maybe during that period he
OL,18,Fdisappeared and no one was aware that
OL,19,Fhe was there until that 1600s period.
OL,26,@uD@]OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
