OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779966178
OL,3,CCerne Abbas Giant in Dorset undergoing
OL,4,Cre-chalking early due to climate change
OL,6,F"But we still don't know why he's
OL,7,Fthere and why they created him and
OL,8,Fthat's a mystery."
OL,10,FThe figure and its wildlife recently
OL,11,Fentered a new chapter, as the National
OL,12,FTrust secured ownership of more than
OL,13,F130 hectares of land surrounding the
OL,14,FGiant just months ago.
OL,16,FThe appeal, backed by Sir Stephen Fry,
OL,17,Freached its #330,000 target in just 60
OL,18,Fdays and will now secure the
OL,19,Fprotection of species like the Duke of
OL,20,FBurgundy butterfly on the site of
OL,21,Fspecial scientific interest.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]
